jekts "Europa" und Grundlagenfragen des Rechts beschäftigen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 7aLAW / International.2bisacsh1 aArnold, Stefan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aArnold, Stefan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGutmann, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHerresthal, Carsten, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKähler, Lorenz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLurger, Brigitta, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRiesenhuber, Karl, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET RECHTSWISSENSCHAFTEN 2013z9783110317190oZDB-23-DGC40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978386653975440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783866539754423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783866539754/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGCb2013  aZDB-23-DGGb2013  aZDB-23-GLAc2000d2014